COVID-19 Status

As of 7:21AM PT today, over 1.4 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 25.2 thousand have died.

In the last day, 477 new infections were reported and 3 deaths. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 21 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 58.1% have their 1st shot and 5% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 3 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~8 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ should have the first dose by Jul-11 and fully vaccinated by Sep-05. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
